{"tid":926669,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鐵甲威龍1-2","createTime":"2018-12-03T15:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T19:03:24.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b93d7d5eda4f01cdb4532427a4c657795a4a0a","tid":926669,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=YW0FpnfMJI%2BsLu9EGGNxA%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=66c69261\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=YW0FpnfMJI%2BsLu9EGGNxA%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f0f9dff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=YW0FpnfMJI%2BsLu9EGGNxA%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=9dc2c465\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/50/Robocop_film.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F50%2FRobocop_film.jpg&h=ebe6a680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.底特律市罪案不斷發生，因警方無完善裝置，市政府於是請總消費產業公司OCP負責製造精良裝置，OCP公司所製造出之裝置造成警員多人死傷於是引起警方反彈。墨菲調職到底特律警局和露意絲搭擋，出勤時正好遇上以卡蘭斯為首的搶匪，二人寡不敵眾，墨菲因此而傷重不治，此時OCP公司的副總裁鮑伯提出機器戰警計劃，墨菲遭改造並洗去記憶，經過各種測試後，戰警出勤打擊犯罪成效良好，鮑伯因此獲得上司青睞<br />\n<br />\n2.在這部續集中，生產機械戰警的泛消費公司掌控著底特律城的治安，警察們因薪水遲遲不能到位而舉行罷工。凱恩（Tom Noonan 飾）旗下的犯罪集團依靠製造風靡各地的毒品&ldquo;紐克&rdquo;大發橫財，社會治安極度敗壞，到處是暴力事件。機械警察墨菲（Peter Weller 飾）追查毒品，將凱恩的製毒工廠搗毀，由此被凱恩團伙埋伏，慘遭肢解。與此同時，泛消費公司趁市政府財務困難，憑合同欲將城市行政納入公司範疇，泛消費的新機械戰警開發計劃屢屢失敗，於是請到心理學家菲克斯參與設計，菲克斯改動墨菲的命令程序使其無法如常工作，從錯誤程序擺脫出來的墨菲帶領一干熱血幹警橫掃凱恩總部，但是菲克斯卻將凱恩改造成為巨大的機械戰警，墨菲與凱恩的再次戰鬥不可避免&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=YW0FpnfMJI%2BsLu9EGGNxA%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8317df6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=YW0FpnfMJI%2BsLu9EGGNxA%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=352ea5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d17e9003287c88c8ab18d0cec0055ccb69a3bc2","tid":926669,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44604fa4f43c5e061fc0bf68e37d62eed694a1a7","tid":926669,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048